    <h1>Rhetoric</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Aristotle &middot; ~350 BCE &middot; <a href="http://classics.mit.edu/Aristotle/rhetoric.html">full text (MIT Classics, public domain)</a></p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">Persuasion has exactly three available means: the character of the speaker, the emotional state of the audience, and the argument itself. Every speech deploys some combination of the three. The Sophists treated this as a bag of tricks. Aristotle treated it as a theory.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SVG: Three modes of persuasion converging on belief change -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-6">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 420 200" class="w-full max-w-lg" style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;">
        <!-- Ethos branch -->
        <circle cx="70" cy="40" r="24" fill="#60a5fa" fill-opacity="0.1" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
        <text x="70" y="36" text-anchor="middle" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.8">ethos</text>
        <text x="70" y="48" text-anchor="middle" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="7" fill-opacity="0.5">character</text>
        <line x1="94" y1="52" x2="200" y2="95" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>

        <!-- Pathos branch -->
        <circle cx="70" cy="110" r="24" fill="#f59e0b" fill-opacity="0.1" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
        <text x="70" y="106" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.8">pathos</text>
        <text x="70" y="118" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="7" fill-opacity="0.5">emotion</text>
        <line x1="94" y1="110" x2="200" y2="102" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>

        <!-- Logos branch -->
        <circle cx="70" cy="170" r="24" fill="#34d399" fill-opacity="0.1" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
        <text x="70" y="166" text-anchor="middle" fill="#34d399" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.8">logos</text>
        <text x="70" y="178" text-anchor="middle" fill="#34d399" font-size="7" fill-opacity="0.5">argument</text>
        <line x1="94" y1="164" x2="200" y2="108" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>

        <!-- Convergence point -->
